Lo somabhizinisi odabuka eZimbabwe, kuthiwa utholwe umsebenzi wakhe elele edamini legazi. Okhulumela abenkampani yonogada iReaction Unit South Africa (Rusa), uMnuz Prem Balram, uthe izolo ngabo 9:46 ekuseni babizelwe kule ndawo yebhizinisi emuva kokuthi umsebenzi ethole umqashi wakhe elele edamini legazi lapho besebenzela khona. Kuthiwa lo msebenzi ubethi uyobheka abekuzwe kuqhuma kule ndawo athole kuyo umqashi wakhe. UBalram uthe ngesikhathi befika abezimo eziphuthumayo, bathole lo somabhizinisi elimele emuva kokushaywa yinsimbi. Kuthiwa ubeyedwa ngesikhathi ehlelwa yile ngozi. Uthe amaphoyisa afikile endaweni yesehlo ukuze aphenye.